[% WRAPPER layout.tt title="Disnix support" menu='disnix' %]

<p>If you run into problems with Disnix, there are a few ways to get help:</p>

<ul>
  
  <li>You can drop by on the <strong>IRC channel</strong> <a
  href="irc://irc.freenode.net/#nixos"><tt>#nixos</tt></a> on <a
  href="https://freenode.net/"><tt>irc.freenode.net</tt></a>.</li>

  <li>You can use the <strong>mailing list</strong> <a
  href="http://lists.science.uu.nl/mailman/listinfo/nix-dev"><tt>nix-dev@lists.science.uu.nl</tt></a>.</li>
  
  <li>You can <strong>report bugs</strong> in the <a
  href="https://github.com/svanderburg/disnix/issues">Disnix issue
  tracker</a>.</li>
  
</ul>

[% END %]
